2025-12-09
- Styled home sections (Services Snapshot, Why Choose, Industries, Portfolio, Testimonials, CTA) with rounded bottoms, gradient backgrounds, and AIO-inspired headings.
- Added soft glow/mesh overlays and badges for section headers to align with NxTech teal/cyan theme.
