2025-12-15
- Designed and implemented initial Prisma schema for core backend entities (users, services, industries, portfolio, case studies, testimonials, achievements/certifications, blog categories, blogs, team, contact submissions, and quote requests) backed by PostgreSQL.
- Validated Prisma schema via `npx prisma validate` to ensure relations and enums compile correctly.
- Integrated NextAuth with credential-based admin login, Prisma adapter usage, JWT sessions, secure cookies, middleware protection for dashboard routes, and an admin-only sign-in page.
 - Added Prisma seed script to create an initial admin user (admin@nts.com / Admin@123) via `npx prisma db seed`.


